column21: Crop Yield lb/ac for NRC or NEC

column2: Manure Test and Nitrogen Calculated Value:
Formula or Nutrient Source for Planned Crop
a. Cover crop contributed more than 3,500 lb DM/ac during last six months after harvesting
b. Manure applied during the last 24 months provide at least 50 lb N/Ac
c. Fertilizer rate applied in previous crop exceeds nitrogen crop removal not less than 22 lb N/Ac during last six months after harvesting.
d. Soil organic level is more than 4% in soils with more than 30% clay; > 2.5% for others soil texture
e. Dissolved inorganic nitrogen is more than 25 mg NO3 - NKg soil
